  "10 g/L of salt was dissolved in the solution": "",
  "100 g/L of salt was dissolved in the solution": "",
  "200 mL = 0.2 L. Concentration = 10 g / 0.2 L = 50 g/L. The student had 10 grams of salt in 0.2 liters of solution.": "",
  "A student makes sweet tea by adding 3 tablespoons of sugar. Her friend adds 6 tablespoons of sugar to the same amount of tea. Whose tea is more concentrated?": "",
